\par\par \b \uc2  2001 Growth target attainable - Econit. \b0\par\par\uc2 503 \uc2 words\par \uc2 5 September 2001\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  12 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA (JP): Despite an expected weaker export performance, the government could still achieve its 2001 \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth target of 3-3.5 percent on the back of rapidly growing domestic consumption and gross investment, the private think tank Econit said on Tuesday. \par \par \uc2  Deputy managing director of the Jakarta-based advisory body Hendri Saprini said that the two indicators had been the main contributors to the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  growth during the first two quarters and the trend seemed to continue toward the next semester. \par \par \uc2  She explained that while net-export growth showed a declining trend in the first two quarters, domestic consumption, investment inflow and government \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  grew at a comfortable rate of 8.38 percent in the second quarter of this year, compared to 4.69 percent in the same period last year. \par \par \uc2  Hendri said that the weaker export growth was mainly due to the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  slowdown in the country's major export destinations including Japan and the U.S. \par \par \uc2  She added, however, that the country's lack of competitiveness in the international market also played a part in the export growth downturn. \par \par \uc2  The expected the \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  slowdown in the country's major trading partners had earlier raised concern that the government might not be able to meet its 2001 growth target. \par \par \uc2  As the current \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  and political situation appears to be heading in the right direction, domestic consumption was expected to improve significantly in the second semester, Econit said. \par \par \uc2  It said that the highest growth for the year would likely occur in the last quarter, with two festivities: the Muslim new year, Idul Fitri, and Christmas celebrations falling in the same month. \par \par \uc2  Domestic consumption in the first and second quarter increased by 5.9 percent and 4.6 percent respectively, compared to the corresponding periods last year, Econit said. \par \par \uc2  Beside domestic consumption, gross investment would also play a crucial role in the country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  recovery as it had been able to maintain its high growth of more than 15 percent for the last five quarters despite the political \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertainty\b0 \highlight\uc2  during the period, Econit said. \par \par \uc2  Elsewhere, Hendri called on the government to take advantage of the above improving indicators. \par \par \uc2  "The real sector's performance in the first semester has been outstanding. The government should give full support by issuing more favorable \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2 ," she told reporters. \par \par \uc2  "And the current tight money \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  is certainly not helping," she added, referring to the much-criticized high interest rate \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  of \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  said earlier that it would maintain its tight monetary \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  for the time being despite the month-on-month deflation of 0.21 percent in August, citing inflationary pressure remained a worry. \par \par \uc2  The interest rate for \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 's one-month SBI promissory notes is currently at 17.67 percent. \par \par \uc2  "The interest rate at the moment is rather too high for the business community and I am hopeful that \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  will evaluate their \b \highlight22\uc2 policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  sometime soon," Hendri said.(10) \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020010905dx950000m\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw298\pich36\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal4470\pichgoal540
