\par\par \b \uc2  BI could double intervention in forex market. \b0\par\par\uc2 526 \uc2 words\par \uc2 11 October 2001\par \uc2 Jakarta Post\par \uc2 JKPOST\par  20 \par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 The Jakarta Post\par \par \uc2  Berni K. Moestafa, The Jakarta Post, Jakarta \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  (BI) said it was ready to double the volume of its intervention in the foreign exchange market, in an apparent emergency move to defend the rupiah from the impact of the war raging in Afghanistan. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  governor Sjahril Sabirin said on Wednesday the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  would proceed with interventionist measures as they showed positive results. \par \par \uc2  "BI, therefore, may double the amount of funds needed for the intervention effort, to speed up the strengthening of the rupiah," he was quoted as saying by AFX-Asia newswires. He did not reveal the value of the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2 's previous intervention. \par \par \uc2  Without further intervention, he said, the rupiah would extend its downward fall. \par \par \uc2  According to him, aggressive moves are necessary because the rupiah is undervalued. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril said earlier that the rupiah's fundamental value ranged between 7,500 to 8,000 against the U.S. dollar. \par \par \uc2  The local unit was still trading below 10,000 on Wednesday, though slightly stronger than it was on Monday. \par \par \uc2  That day, the rupiah tumbled to 10,500 as the market reacted to the U.S-led attack against Afghanistan on Sunday night. \par \par \uc2  The rupiah recovered to 9,980 late Wednesday due to what some believed was dollar selling by state banks acting on behalf of \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Sjahril said earlier that the \b \highlight22\uc2 central bank\b0 \highlight\uc2  had adequate foreign exchange \b \highlight22\uc2 reserves\b0 \highlight\uc2  to back up further intervention. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Bank Indonesia\b0 \highlight\uc2  said its foreign exchange \b \highlight22\uc2 reserves\b0 \highlight\uc2  as of last Friday stood at US$28.952 billion, or slightly down from $28.957 billion a week earlier. \par \par \uc2  Sjahril's statements follow Minister of Finance Boediono saying earlier this week that more incursions into the money market had become ineffective. \par \par \b \highlight22\uc2 Uncertainties\b0 \highlight\uc2  on the global front, compounded by anti-U.S. rallies at home, gave way to speculation against the rupiah. \par \par \uc2  The global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  outlook worsened from bleak to hopeless after last month's terrorist attacks in the U.S. \par \par \uc2  In the face of this, the government promised emergency measures to ease the impact of a prolonged global \b \highlight22\uc2 economic\b0 \highlight\uc2  slump but has thus far remained silent about actions being adopted to revitalize the domestic \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  It has ruled out a \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal stimulus\b0 \highlight\uc2  package due to this and next year's tight state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 . \par \par \uc2  Boediono, however, suggested raising development \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  for rural economies. \par \par \uc2  "From the (\b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2 's) \b \highlight22\uc2 spending\b0 \highlight\uc2  side, we can direct limited \b \highlight22\uc2 stimulus\b0 \highlight\uc2 , though not for large (industry) sectors," he said prior to a meeting with the \b \highlight22\uc2 House of Representatives\b0 \highlight\uc2 ' state \b \highlight22\uc2 budget\b0 \highlight\uc2  commission. \par \par \uc2  Boediono said Indonesia's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  would benefit more from a multiplier effect injected through rural economies. \par \par \uc2  "One rupiah in the hands of small income groups usually circulates faster at home than if we spend it on imports," he explained. \par \par \uc2  Elsewhere, State Minister for National Development Planning Kwik Kian Gie said the government was too poor for a \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal stimulus\b0 \highlight\uc2  package. \par \par \uc2  "The best we can do is for the government to become more efficient," he said. \par \par \uc2  The country's \b \highlight22\uc2 economy\b0 \highlight\uc2  would have to rely on industries with a healthy local market share for stimulating growth, he added. \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020011011dxab0000e\par }\page {\par\fs20\b \uc2  Property shares remain bearish. \b0\par\par\uc2 211 \uc2 words\par \uc2 12 October 2001\par \uc2 Bisnis Indonesia\par \uc2 BISNIS\par \uc2 English\par \uc2 (c) 2001 Bisnis Indonesia\par \par \uc2  JAKARTA: Transactions on property shares remained bearish last week. \par \par \uc2  Investors remained cautious carrying out transactions amid escalating global \par \par \uc2  political tensions following the US and British military aggression to \par \par \uc2  Afghanistan. \par \par \uc2  Investors are also concerned about actions of certain Islam organizations \par \par \uc2  and decided to sell property shares to secure investments. The selling \par \par \uc2  pressure was also triggered by the recent rupiah depreciation against the US \par \par \uc2  dollar. \par \par \uc2  The property shares fell 2.64% with transaction volume reaching 71.037 \par \par \uc2  million units valuing Rp7.080 billion. Five shares gained, 10 lost, and 18 \par \par \uc2  were stagnant. Meanwhile, Lamicitra Nusantara gained the highest transaction \par \par \uc2  value of Rp3.484 billion. The property index shed 3.75% to 24.861 (09 \par \par \uc2  October) from 25.830 (02 October). The JSX composite index also fell 1.97% \par \par \uc2  to 369.797. 