th an \b \highlight22\uc2 uncertain policy\b0 \highlight\uc2  environment, limited \b \highlight22\uc2 fiscal\b0 \highlight\uc2  flexibility, a weak currency, and rising inflation; Standard & Poor's considers that although the risk of systemwide exchange controls being imposed is not immaterial in Indonesia, this risk is consistent with a single-'B'-minus rating." \par \par \uc2  Copyright 2001 The Jakarta Post. \par \par \uc2 Document jkpost0020011203dxc1000bo\par }\page {\par\fs20{\*\shppict{\pict\pngblip\picw139\pich40\picscaley100\picscalex100\picwgoal2085\pichgoal600
